# Silicon Valley Trail — Environment Variables
#
# GOOD NEWS: This game currently requires NO API keys!
# Open-Meteo (the weather API) is completely free and keyless.
#
# For local development with keys, copy this file to `.env` (same folder) and fill in values.
# `.env` is listed in the repo-root `.gitignore` and must never be committed.
#
# The app loads variables via `com.siliconvalleytrail.Env#get`:
#   - OS environment variables take precedence (good for CI and production).
#   - Then values from `.env` in the working directory (usually this project folder).
#
# IMPORTANT: NEVER commit actual API keys to GitHub.

# Example (not currently used by the game):
# OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_key_here
